{"id":"5e9c061f774c2610387e4e38","title":"Artist Profile: Yussef Hu","content":"<p>Situated in a room looking like something out of an episode of Dexter.</p><p> <b>Yuseff Hu,</b> tired and probably nauseous, staggers round the room full of nervously laughing spectators, preparing for each stage of his performance, <b><i>Resting on a sharp point</i></b><i>.<b> </b>2013<b></b></i></p>\n<p>The task executed is to spear what looks like massive carcass sacks filled with balloons pumped full of ketchup, mayonnaise, mustard and brown sauce. The oozing condiments leak into a bucket placed below this hoisted pack and the artist, gagging and shaking, ingests this readymade burger sauce before repeating the whole process five times.</p>\n<p>I’ve always had a strong stomach, but this tested me. A piece of art that could induce nausea to this degree definitely deserves a mention. I will take my hat off to anyone who could sit through the full 47 minutes.</p>\n<p>For Yussef’s website Click <a href=\"https://yussefhu.com/Resting-on-a-Sharp-Point\"><b>HERE</b></a>.</p>\n<p>The documented performance will be on at the <b>Slade BA/BFA Degree Show</b> until the 23<sup>rd</sup> May.</p>\n<p>For more information Click <a href=\"https://www.ucl.ac.uk/slade/degree2013/\"><strong>HERE</strong></a>.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://api.crackintheroad.com/arts/21980-artist-profile-yussef-hu/attachment/yuseff-hu/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-21981\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-21981\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://admin.crackintheroad.com/uploads/2013/05/yuseff-hu.jpg\" srcset=\"https://api.crackintheroad.com/images/2013/05/yuseff-hu.jpg 2048w, https://api.crackintheroad.com/images/2013/05/yuseff-hu-300x200.jpg 300w, https://api.crackintheroad.com/images/2013/05/yuseff-hu-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://api.crackintheroad.com/images/2013/05/yuseff-hu-50x33.jpg 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://admin.crackintheroad.com/arts/21980-artist-profile-yussef-hu/attachment/yuseff-hu4/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-21983\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-21983\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://api.crackintheroad.com/images/2013/05/yuseff-hu4.jpg\" srcset=\"https://api.crackintheroad.com/images/2013/05/yuseff-hu4.jpg 2048w, https://api.crackintheroad.com/images/2013/05/yuseff-hu4-300x200.jpg 300w, https://api.crackintheroad.com/images/2013/05/yuseff-hu4-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://api.crackintheroad.com/images/2013/05/yuseff-hu4-50x33.jpg 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://admin.crackintheroad.com/arts/21980-artist-profile-yussef-hu/attachment/yuseff-hu5/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-21984\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-21984\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://api.crackintheroad.com/images/2013/05/yuseff-hu5.jpg\" srcset=\"https://api.crackintheroad.com/images/2013/05/yuseff-hu5.jpg 2048w, https://api.crackintheroad.com/images/2013/05/yuseff-hu5-300x199.jpg 300w, https://api.crackintheroad.com/images/2013/05/yuseff-hu5-1024x680.jpg 1024w, https://api.crackintheroad.com/images/2013/05/yuseff-hu5-50x33.jpg 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://admin.crackintheroad.com/arts/21980-artist-profile-yussef-hu/attachment/yuseffhu6/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-21985\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-21985\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://api.crackintheroad.com/images/2013/05/yuseffhu6.jpg\" srcset=\"https://api.crackintheroad.com/images/2013/05/yuseffhu6.jpg 2048w, https://api.crackintheroad.com/images/2013/05/yuseffhu6-300x200.jpg 300w, https://api.crackintheroad.com/images/2013/05/yuseffhu6-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://api.crackintheroad.com/images/2013/05/yuseffhu6-50x33.jpg 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px\" /></a></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://admin.crackintheroad.com/arts/21980-artist-profile-yussef-hu/attachment/yuseffhu8/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-21987\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-21987\" alt=\"\" src